Package WheeledVehicle

Class WheeledTransportation

java.lang.Object
Superclass.Vehicle
WheeledVehicle.WheeledTransportation
Direct Known Subclasses:
Monowheel, Train
public class WheeledTransportation
extends Vehicle
The WheeledTransportation class is designed to contain the most basic attributes/methods which any wheeled vehicle should possess.
Author:
Kcour
